snippet.title: Islands of the Caliph Trailer
snippet.description:
Islands of the Caliph is an old school RPG based on Medieval Middle-Eastern folklore and culture.

Learn more here: https://schmidt-workshops.itch.io/islands-of-the-caliph

The beautiful music was composed and recorded by Ronnie Malley: https://ronniemalley.com

Video produced by Chris Lohr: https://www.thechrislohrvg.com/
